ActNational Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order
PrecisReappointment of CLARENCE JOSEPH LOUIE of Oliver, British Columbia, to be a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of CLARENCE JOSEPH LOUIE as Vice-Chairperson of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board; effective April 24, 2004.
